rspec_tour.description: Variable number of nodes in a lan. You have the option of picking from one of several standard images we provide, or just use the default (typically a recent version of Ubuntu). You may also optionally pick the specific hardware type for all the nodes in the lan.
rspec_tour.instructions: Wait for the experiment to start, and then log into one or more of the nodes by clicking on them in the toplogy, and choosing the `shell` menu option. Use `sudo` to run root commands.
